[
    {
        "text": "This was a scene in Ishinomaki on that fateful day.",
        "startTime": 7887,
        "endTime": 11478,
        "slowStartTime": 11981,
        "slowEndTime": 17442
    },
    {
        "text": "The coastal city was one of the hardest hit,...",
        "startTime": 12609,
        "endTime": 14877,
        "slowStartTime": 19064,
        "slowEndTime": 22540
    },
    {
        "text": "...having lost more than 3,000 residents,...",
        "startTime": 14987,
        "endTime": 17155,
        "slowStartTime": 22631,
        "slowEndTime": 25957
    },
    {
        "text": "...84 of them were lost at this one school.",
        "startTime": 17793,
        "endTime": 20362,
        "slowStartTime": 26840,
        "slowEndTime": 30768
    },
    {
        "text": "Noriki lost his twelve-year-old daughter here in the 2011 tsunami.",
        "startTime": 20869,
        "endTime": 24871,
        "slowStartTime": 31453,
        "slowEndTime": 37532
    },
    {
        "text": "This behind me is what remains of her Okawa Elementary School where she attended.",
        "startTime": 24967,
        "endTime": 29909,
        "slowStartTime": 37600,
        "slowEndTime": 45088
    },
    {
        "text": "The water then came up to where that white sign is up on that hill...",
        "startTime": 30152,
        "endTime": 33933,
        "slowStartTime": 45378,
        "slowEndTime": 51124
    },
    {
        "text": "...and if the 84 of them had just evacuated above that white sign,...",
        "startTime": 34017,
        "endTime": 38761,
        "slowStartTime": 51175,
        "slowEndTime": 58366
    },
    {
        "text": "...then their lives could have been saved.",
        "startTime": 38860,
        "endTime": 40995,
        "slowStartTime": 58440,
        "slowEndTime": 61717
    },
    {
        "text": "Instead, the teachers led the students this way, the wrong direction,...",
        "startTime": 41611,
        "endTime": 45776,
        "slowStartTime": 62567,
        "slowEndTime": 68889
    },
    {
        "text": "...because this is a dead end and that's where the waves crashed over them.",
        "startTime": 45860,
        "endTime": 50555,
        "slowStartTime": 68940,
        "slowEndTime": 76058
    },
    {
        "text": "Noriki wants the world to know what happened here...",
        "startTime": 51900,
        "endTime": 54375,
        "slowStartTime": 78000,
        "slowEndTime": 81787
    },
    {
        "text": "...and says the Olympics torch relay was the perfect opportunity.",
        "startTime": 54462,
        "endTime": 58330,
        "slowStartTime": 81843,
        "slowEndTime": 87720
    },
    {
        "text": "He applied and was selected as one of the torchbearers...",
        "startTime": 59046,
        "endTime": 62319,
        "slowStartTime": 88719,
        "slowEndTime": 93703
    },
    {
        "text": "...who reflect the Olympic spirit.",
        "startTime": 62403,
        "endTime": 64284,
        "slowStartTime": 93754,
        "slowEndTime": 96651
    }
]